{"tid":2487050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用數據話比你聽 點解193寸得起。","createTime":"2021-04-13T09:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:07:02.000Z","uid":176532,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65abcf83a1671d08c268e40a9f871254eb399f31","tid":2487050,"uid":176532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">付費平台 Viutv vs Tvb</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Viutv</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1082050&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1082050%26newssource%3DHK6&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=44d5d409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1082050&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n電盈(<a href=\"http://00008.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00008.HK&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=fdded573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00008.HK</a>)指，根據AMPD 2020年第四季研究報告中，旗下泛區域OTT串流視象平台Viu於東南亞(印尼、菲律賓、新加坡及泰國)主要視象平台中，每月活躍用戶人數排名第一。於2020年12月，Viu每月活躍用戶達4,500萬名。<br />\n<br />\n按付費用戶及串流分鐘計算，Viu 於東南亞主要視象平台中均位列第二。Viu首席業務總監(亞洲)仇婉君表示，報告預計網上視象串流市場未來三年市場複合年增長率將高達26%，認為Viu聚焦亞洲內容、建立強大夥伴關係，可持續吸引東南亞的訂戶及廣告商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1075487&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1075487%26newssource%3DHK6&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=fa278961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1075487&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n公司指，付費用戶於去年錄得47%的按年升幅。Viu 在變現方面亦取得高增長，當中訂閱收益按年躍升62%，成為推動整體營業額增加30%的主要動力來源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tvb</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1085635&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1085635%26newssource%3DHK6&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=551bfed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1085635&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n電視廣播(<a href=\"http://00511.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00511.HK&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=157c7abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00511.HK</a>)公布截至2020年12月底止年度業績顯示，錄得股東應佔虧損為2.81億元，上年同期虧損為2.95億元；基本每股虧損為0.64元，不派末期息。上年同期派息0.5元。<br />\n<br />\n期內，總收入按年減少25%至27.24億元。總成本按年跌12%至32.53億元。無綫電視數碼平台的非廣告收入總額按年增加8%至5.52億元。<br />\n期內，myTV SUPER業務分部錄得盈利1,100萬元，上年同期盈利為4,000萬元，盈利減少由於廣告收入較疲弱所致。大台網及電子商貿業務分部(包括Big Big Shop)錄得盈利按年增20%至5,300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">廣告收入Viutv vs Tvb </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Viutv</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1074761&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1074761%26newssource%3DHK6&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=51eb1b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1074761&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n雖然本地廣告消費收縮，不過ViuTV每月平均觀眾有所增加，去年廣告收益增長29%至2.71億元，男團MIRROR及ERROR通過《全民造星》系列引起公眾留意，並越來越受歡迎，有助公司藝人管理業務發展。他指出近年ViuTV在競爭激烈情況下透過本地製作的節目吸引觀眾，加上公司亦與廣告商有良好合作，除廣告收入增長外，市場份額也有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tvb</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1085635&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1085635%26newssource%3DHK6&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=551bfed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1085635&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n香港電視廣播分部的廣告收入按年減少54%至8.81億元。<br />\nmyTV SUPER業務分部錄得盈利1,100萬元，上年同期盈利為4,000萬元，盈利減少由於廣告收入較疲弱所致。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">公司股價 Viutv vs Tvb </span></span><br />\nViutv  屬李澤楷旗下 多家子母公母<br />\n只選取 00008電訊盈科 作參考 <br />\n現市值約 <span class=\"red\">344.74億</span><br />\n<br />\nTvb 現 市值 <span class=\"red\">38.81億</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論: 三爺背景係李澤楷，你tvb 蚊滋公司 邊個會驚你啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"ec3ca5bd0f2cf3a8bc44a9c70e0f899bb0d6d3a3","tid":2487050,"uid":176532,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">TLDR</span></span> <br />\n講公司背景 193 所屬公司 勝<br />\n講業績 193 所屬公司 勝<br />\n講市值  193 所屬公司 勝<br />\n講人氣 193勝<br />\n講高度 193勝<br />\n講廢話 193勝<br />\n講靚仔 193勝 <br />\n講心地 193勝<br />\n講年紀 193勝<br />\n<br />\n你間TVB 市值少過人地9倍 <br />\n生意老婆又比人搶埋<br />\n<br />\n堂堂大台 做到個數據咁差 <br />\n點同我33仔鬥？ <br />\n<br />\n三爺就咁企喺到都贏你9個頭<br />\n你老母豆潤公司仔<br />\n唔寸你 寸邊個？"},{"pid":"d4c62abae9efd2a7c1ea8f2b8f366e675b1f140a","tid":2487050,"uid":176532,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"我係唔會用193個高度做數據去解釋佢寸得起<br />\n太膚淺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1066c07197c60329eee8bba4a729e8a0e6d989a5","tid":2487050,"uid":176532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"newgod 美c入嚟講下<br />\n點解你公司生意失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff3cd1828a719c72073a9b03c7c640800aecca1","tid":2487050,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"df36865c9af57ed32a9feac161048acc9bfe60a6","tid":2487050,"uid":85864,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec3ca5bd0f2cf3a8bc44a9c70e0f899bb0d6d3a3","tid":2487050,"uid":176532,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span cl